text: Paulina Paszek (born 26 October 1997) is a Polish sprint canoeist. She participated at the 2018 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships, winning a medal.K-2 1000 m results ==References== Category:Living people Category:1997 births Category:Polish female canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:Sportspeople from Bielsko-Biała
